title: The Untapped Secret to Your Power, & Sex Appeal
description:
In this bonus episode I share a live talk from 2011 I’ll teach you to connect to your most untapped resource;.  — just by being you! In this live talk, I’ll reveal the exact steps you can take to recognize who you really are (instead of who you think you should be) so you can live with more confidence and power. When you unleash this untapped energy you become a Super Attractor!
 

The following are helpful resources and books I mention within the episode: 


If you want more guidance on fearlessly honoring your truth, check out my latest book Happy Days: The Guided Path from Trauma to Profound Freedom and Inner Peace. This will help you honor your true life story, recognize that you are not a victim … and believe in happy days ahead. https://bit.ly/39dXEeJ


Want even more support? I created the Miracle Membership to help you design a spiritual practice you can stick to—so you can feel connected, supported and inspired every day. Each week I deliver brand new workshops, guided meditations, live group meditations, community connection, and so much more. Plus, it’s easy to access on your phone, computer or tablet. Click here to join. https://bit.ly/3NR4W6U


If you feel you need more support, please refer to this list of  mental health resources. I’m proud of you for being here. https://bit.ly/3aWoh8x


This podcast is intended to educate, inspire and support you on your personal journey towards inner peace. I am not a psychologist or a medical doctor and do not offer any professional health or medical advice. If you are suffering from any psychological  or medical conditions, please seek help from  a qualified health professional.

 

Go to WHOOP.com and use code "GABBY" to save 15% and get free shipping automatically applied today.

 

Produced by Dear Media.
